49:52.700 --> 49:56.666
HALL: Deep and the stories.

49:56.966 --> 49:58.333
You're not going to believe it.

49:58.366 --> 50:00.266
GATES: Yeah.

50:00.633 --> 50:02.200
HALL: She probably won't.

