51:14.433 --> 51:16.700
Would you please turn the page?

51:18.766 --> 51:21.566
DANIELS: No. No!

51:21.600 --> 51:23.166
GATES: Yes. Absolutely.

51:23.200 --> 51:24.342
DANIELS: How is this possible?

